## 📊 Exploratory Data Analysis

The project includes:

* Dataset Overview
* Data Types Inspection
* Missing Values Analysis
* Duplicate Values Check
* Summary Statistics
* Numerical Feature Analysis
* Categorical Feature Analysis
* Income Distribution
* Age Distribution
* Gender Analysis
* Education Analysis
* Occupation Analysis
* Income vs Gender
* Income vs Education
* Correlation Heatmap
* Outlier Detection using Boxplots

